---
title: Carb Smart Fiesta Double Pork Salad with Charred Corn Salsa and Chipotle Crema
description: Sweet, spicy and tangy flavours hold court in this recipe! Ground pork is sautéed in smoky Tex-Mex paste, then tossed over fresh spring mix studded with charred corn and tomato salsa. A cooling chipotle crema brings a welcome brightness!
